## HyperFrames agent — media MCP (bắt buộc phase render)

- Đọc: `.cursor/skills/biong-short-video-hyperframes/references/media-mcp-activation.md` + `visual-shot-plan.md`
- Phase render: `search_bgm` + `search_giphy` + stock **bg only** theo shot-plan; mỗi beat = `hyperframes/prompts/{hf_prompt_type}.md` (hf-seek)
- `media-plan.md`: sfx_hook + bgm_global + `hf_prompt_type`/accent/bg mỗi beat
- `/continuous-motion` → ambient-layer + `window.__timelines["ambient"]`
- Beat HTML: hf-seek `render()` pure function of `t` — đọc `hf-prompt-beat-contract.md`
- Ambient only: GSAP `paused: true` + `window.__timelines["ambient"]`; cấm `tl.play()`; cấm GSAP beat timeline

## HyperFrames agent — auto-evolution (bắt buộc phase render)

- Đọc TRƯỚC beat HTML: `.cursor/skills/biong-short-video-hyperframes/references/evolution-memory.md`
- Sau preflight pass: `/biong-short-video-evolution` — snapshot + vision audit + tự vá (max 2 vòng, không hỏi user)
- Sau vision pass: append `evolution-memory.md` + `assets/visual-audit-report.json`
- Cấm sửa `SKILL.md` trong session render; cấm `render --quality high` trước vision pass